Bimwebimwe mu bikoresho bikoreshwa muri uwo mugwi birashobora mbere guhindura ibisomwa vyo mu ndimi z’inyamahanga ku bimenyetso canke ku bindi bintu vy’ukuri vyo kw’isi igihe nyene kubikoresha yerekeje kuri ayo matelefone kuri ivyo bintu.
Imoteri z’ubuhinduzi zararyohowe bimwe bitangaje, kandi ubu kenshi ziratanga impinduro zitari nke canke nke zitagiramwo amakosa (kandi ni gake cane zikoreshwa mu vy’ubuhinduzi), mugabo hari ukuntu bikenewe ko zitwararikwa, kubera ko zishobora kuba zigifise amakosa yose.
Kimwe mu bintu bimenyerewe kuruta ibindi muri ivyo ni Ubuhinduzi bwitwa Google, ivyo bikaba bituma Bibiliya ihindurwa hataboneka iyo umuntu amaze kuvoma amakuru y’ururimi yipfuza.
Gukoresha porogarama za GPS zigufasha kuyobora abantu kuri telefone ni bwo buryo bworoshe kandi bworoshe kuruta ubundi bwose bwo gukoresha igihe uri mu gihugu cawe c’amavukiro.
Irashobora kuziganya amahera atarinze kugura amakarata mashasha kugira ngo ikoreshwe n’imashini yitwa GPS, canke ngo ikoreshwe n’igikoresho co gukotesha imodoka canke ngo ikoreshwe mw’ishirahamwe rikotesha umuduga.
Nimba udafise amakuru ajanye na telefone yawe, canke igihe ataba agikora neza, ivyo bakora birashobora kuba bike canke ntibiboneke.
